(18, 'HIKING TOOLS', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>হাইকিং মানেই যে শুধু বিরাট আয়োজন ও প্ল্যানিং তা কিন্তু নয়।</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>অ্যাডভেঞ্চার উপভোগের জন্য হাইকিং হতে পারে একদিনেরও। সেক্ষেত্রে সাথে যা যা নিতে হবে তা হলো-</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>(১) ম্যাপ (২) ফ্ল্যাশলাইট (৩) ব্যাটারি (৪) প্যাকেটজাত হালকা খাবার (৫) লাইটার (৬) মিনি ওয়াটার ফিল্টার (৭) ওয়াটারপ্রুফ ব্যাগ (৮) রেইনকোট (৯) হাঁটার উপযোগী পানি নিরোধক জুতা ও (১০) কম্পাস।</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 4, '2019/01/post.jpg', 1, 1, 0, '[24]', '2019-02-03 03:45:48', NULL),
(19, 'Cycling alone - from Malaysia to Thailand', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>“When the spirits are\nlow, when the day appears dark, when work becomes monotonous, when hope hardly\nseems worth having, just mount a bicycle and go out for a spin down the road,\nwithout thought on anything but the ride you are taking.” —&nbsp;</em><strong><em>Arthur Conan Doyle,\nBritish author</em></strong><em></em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>After\nworking for many years in the corporate world - to find my spirt &amp; reinvent\nmy life - On December 2016, I embarked on a 2000 km solo bicycling adventure in\nSouth East Asia from Kualalumpur, Malaysia to Bangkok, Thailand.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The\nmission was to raise fund for underprivileged children on behalf of UNICEF.\nAfter starting from KL on 16th December, after riding for 22 days, I reached my\ndestination Bangkok. Here are the top learnings of my solo cycling from\nKualalumpur to Bangkok.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>1.THE PRE-STRATEGY IS 90% OF THE ADVENTURE… REST 10% IS FUN:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>All\nthe small &amp; big decisions I made before starting the ride, proved to be the\nmost critical steps to make the expedition a success – like how to pack my\npanniers for this long ride, how to keep my money safe, route selection and\nplanning accommodation ahead was most critical for making the mission a\nsuccess.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>2.THE WORLD IS MUCH SAFER THAN WE THINK:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I\nheard it from every adventure traveler I met. Back in home we all hear all the\nhorror stories of what may happen on the road &amp; unknown places as a\nstranger… but what I discovered was quite an opposite reality. People were\nembracing me with warmth &amp; happiness – offering me free food &amp; drinks\nas a cyclist! The threat or fear factor I faced was the thing I least\napprehended – it was stray Dogs!!!<strong></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>3.EVEN IF YOU ARE TRAVELLING SOLO… YOU ARE NEVER ALONE:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>If\nyou are kind, friendly &amp; helpful – you can bond with people on the road as\na great team. On my second day I met British cyclist&amp; on our third day we\nmet French velo-adventurers Marion &amp; Maxim. We four – unknown to each other\nbonded as best buddies &amp; rode together till Thai border with indomitable\nspirit – never felt alone for a single moment.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>4.EXPEDITION FOR A CAUSE WORTH EVERY STRUGGLE:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Since\nthe ride was not only an adventure, it was for a cause – people cheered me from\nmy homeland through social media, colleagues around the world wrote me\nencouraging notes &amp; local people I met on the road embraced me with love! –\nAll these positive feedbacks made me forget the gruel of the ride.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>5.PEOPLE AROUND THE WORLD VALUES GOOD WORK:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Before\narranging the mission, I had a suspicion on what people might think about\ncycling for child right – I was expecting both positive &amp; negative\ncomments. To my utter surprise, I received positive comments from around the\nworld. 100% of my fund raising came from colleagues &amp; relatives abroad. And\nmany of them are from the sternest professional I least expected to donate!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<figure class=\"gallery-item\">\n				<a data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"no\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"e5df55b\" href=\"/2019/01/IMG_2969.jpg\"><img width=\"400\" height=\"400\" src=\"/2019/01/IMG_2969-400x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/2019/01/IMG_2969-400x400.jpg 400w, /2019/01/IMG_2969-150x150.jpg 150w, /2019/01/IMG_2969-230x230.jpg 230w, /2019/01/IMG_2969-640x640.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\"></a><br>\n			</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery-item\">\n				<a data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"no\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"e5df55b\" href=\"/2019/01/IMG_2970.jpg\"><img width=\"400\" height=\"400\" src=\"/2019/01/IMG_2970-400x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/2019/01/IMG_2970-400x400.jpg 400w, /2019/01/IMG_2970-150x150.jpg 150w, /2019/01/IMG_2970-230x230.jpg 230w, /2019/01/IMG_2970-640x640.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\"></a><br>\n			</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery-item\">\n				<a data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"no\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"e5df55b\" href=\"/2019/01/IMG_7545.jpg\"><img width=\"400\" height=\"400\" src=\"/2019/01/IMG_7545-400x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/2019/01/IMG_7545-400x400.jpg 400w, /2019/01/IMG_7545-150x150.jpg 150w, /2019/01/IMG_7545-230x230.jpg 230w, /2019/01/IMG_7545-640x640.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\"></a><br>\n			</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery-item\">\n				<a data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"no\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"e5df55b\" href=\"/2019/01/IMG_7546.jpg\"><img width=\"400\" height=\"400\" src=\"/2019/01/IMG_7546-400x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/2019/01/IMG_7546-400x400.jpg 400w, /2019/01/IMG_7546-150x150.jpg 150w, /2019/01/IMG_7546-230x230.jpg 230w, /2019/01/IMG_7546-640x640.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\"></a><br>\n			</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery-item\">\n				<a data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"no\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"e5df55b\" href=\"/2019/01/IMG_7550.jpg\"><img width=\"400\" height=\"400\" src=\"/2019/01/IMG_7550-400x400.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"/2019/01/IMG_7550-400x400.jpg 400w, /2019/01/IMG_7550-150x150.jpg 150w, /2019/01/IMG_7550-230x230.jpg 230w, /2019/01/IMG_7550-640x640.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 